import React from "react"
import { Form, Card } from "react-bootstrap"

function CriticalWarnSelect(props) {
    return (
        <Card>
            <Card.Header>Select The Critical Warnings You Need</Card.Header>
            <Card.Body>
                <Form>
                    <Form.Group>
                        <Form.Check 
                        inline
                        type="checkbox"
                        label="CPR IN PROGRESS"></Form.Check>
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Form.Group>
                        <Form.Check 
                        inline
                        type="checkbox"
                        label="Stroke Alert"></Form.Check>
                    </Form.Group>
                </Form>
            </Card.Body>
        </Card>
    )
}

export default CriticalWarnSelect
